00:34:26.440 --> 00:34:28.519
But Aunt Xiuyun liked them.

00:34:40.280 --> 00:34:41.480
Xiuyun…

00:34:42.840 --> 00:34:44.400
You're too kind.

00:34:46.760 --> 00:34:48.480
You knew everything all along.

00:34:50.239 --> 00:34:52.719
Zhou told you everything too.

00:34:52.719 --> 00:34:53.960
I don't understand

00:34:54.480 --> 00:34:56.960
why you'd still choose this dead end.

00:34:58.760 --> 00:35:00.159
They showed no care at all

00:35:01.840 --> 00:35:03.679
when you died.

00:35:12.599 --> 00:35:14.119
They never once meant

00:35:14.639 --> 00:35:15.920
to hurt Xiuyun.

00:35:16.719 --> 00:35:19.920
In fact, they've been remembering her
in their own ways.

00:35:20.679 --> 00:35:22.559
That cake was from Wu Yunong.

00:35:23.360 --> 00:35:24.840
Even though Hong Lie and Hong Chi

00:35:25.480 --> 00:35:26.760
are barely getting by,

00:35:27.300 --> 00:35:29.440
they still insist on running
a woman's swimming class.

00:35:31.239 --> 00:35:32.840
That's for Xiuyun too.

00:35:33.239 --> 00:35:35.480
The money backing them
comes from Pan Jingting.

00:35:35.559 --> 00:35:37.840
Master Pan wanted
to do his part for her.

00:35:44.079 --> 00:35:45.039
Stop.

00:35:48.239 --> 00:35:49.039
Say no more.

00:35:53.960 --> 00:35:54.760
Elder Yu,

00:35:56.250 --> 00:35:58.500
obsession is like a disease
that clings to your bones.

00:35:59.360 --> 00:36:01.599
It's trapped you here in Rain Manor

00:36:01.719 --> 00:36:02.719
all these years.

00:36:03.679 --> 00:36:04.800
Please try to let it go.

00:36:07.199 --> 00:36:09.239
Your friend asked me to tell you

00:36:09.320 --> 00:36:10.480
